name: Henry the one eyed Lucas
description:
Creative Thinker #3
Henry Lee Lucas; the man, the myth, the legend who was forced to cross dress as a child by his mother so she could pimp him out to women and men. I wish I was making this shit up. No wonder the guy was so fucked in the head. He also ran around with those crazy christians who believed that God would protect them from rattle snake bites. Hallelujah!!!
